{"tid":1448030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:57.000Z","uid":43764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecbc9f26d2e26d6d08de2547011d29d9e7778b73","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」"},{"pid":"6d4f54c440cf8454978519e95c7a4d9664ddfa20","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb560934442e578a22b85b036ffe848fde5460d2","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"367d38a43672f632ba07cde0ab69e7b0efa9d0e5","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a896a14872cbd59f54f3febb45ee8a8b815c3107","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79820c802de2084ba88ef49314a4153169a03db6","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fe7166de75404c615c018101f4ff91d7c5deb90","tid":1448030,"uid":43764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fbfca76df563c1550fe9a581bf41775d0d50111","tid":1448030,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"push"}]}